c: 28
v: 82
t: "Mana balia abekoombanga okhuba shinga ye olwabeele nibachaaka okhuwuka mbu: “eeh koo khane Nyasaye ametanga omukabo ulia owayenya mubasumba bebe, ne atutuyilinjia owayenya, Nyasaye akhayanga okhukholela amalayi liloba liakhakhumilile ninaye, oh toto khane Nyasaye shabusinjia Abakhayi tawe"